{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were so-- so desensitized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It I guess had to be some kind of an elation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not what you expect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were just sort of drifting from one state into the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, it was never ever a real surprise, because-- and I compared notes with some of my friends since then, in recent-- these last four years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all felt the same way, that we had such an unshakable faith in that the good will win and the bad will be punished and that this can only end this way.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we're just-- it's like almost like the end of this terrible fairytale, and then suddenly all is well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we-- we never really suffered psychologically, because we really never believed what was happening, even though the Germans so many times would say things that-- you see that black smoke there?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's your family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or that's who they are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would smell it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we had no reason to doubt it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we just never believed it for a moment, because there was something called the [? 'latrina ?] news' for-- somehow everybody went there, because there was always someone who said, you know what I heard?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's where we got our-- the news information.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they would say, I heard that the mothers and the children and the older people, the little children, were taken to Switzerland, and they are in a sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the word would spread very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they would say, oh, wonderful, as long as they-- they just don't see what we are going through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, through this whole thing, I was keeping a very, very thorough list in my mind of everybody and everybody's name and face who was nice.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
